    <string name="info_text">Ruuvi Station is an easy and powerful tool to superpower RuuviTag sensor nodes.\n
        \nThe application is now in beta and may still have unknown issues. But don’t worry, our team is determined to polish the app to perfection.\n
        \nIf you notice problems or find anything you would like to have changed, please let us know by filling out&#160;<a href="https://ruuvi.typeform.com/to/OEUkXq">this anonymous form</a>.
        \n
        \nQUICK START GUIDE\n
        \n1) Click Add a new RuuviTag from menu and you’re ready to go. Easy as that.\n
        \nGATEWAY\n
        \nCurrently, the gateway feature is for advanced users only. To use it,&#160;<a href="https://github.com/ruuvi/com.ruuvi.station">check the documentation</a>.
        \n
        \nTROUBLESHOOTING\n
        \nRuuviTags are sending temperature data in 0.01 degree resolution. If you see lower accuracy readings for some reason, make sure your RuuviTag is running the latest&#160;<a href="https://lab.ruuvi.com/dfu">Ruuvi Firmware</a>.
        \n
    </string>
